{{page-title 'Combats'}}
<h1>Combats</h1>

<p>The combat directory lists active combats and allows you to view combat status in a web page rather than typing 'combat' over and over in your MUSH window.</p>

<p class="alert alert-info">Usually you'll want to start a combat from the scene menu of an <LinkTo @route="scenes-live">active scene</LinkTo>, so the scene and combat are linked. This ensures that combat results are added to the scene. If you want an orphaned combat, <a href="#" {{action 'startCombat'}}>click here</a> to start one.</p>

<table class="table table-striped">
<thead>
    <th>Combat ID</th>
    <th>Organizer</th>
    <th>Scene</th>
    <th>Participants</th>
</thead>

<tbody>
{{#each model as |combat|}}
<tr><td>
    <LinkTo @route="combat" @model={{combat.id}}>{{combat.id}}</LinkTo>
</td>

<td>
    {{combat.organizer}}
</td>

<td>
  {{#if combat.scene}}
    <LinkTo @route="scene-live" @model={{combat.scene}}>{{combat.scene}}</LinkTo>
  {{/if}}
</td>

<td>
    {{#each combat.participants as |participant|}}
    {{participant}}
    {{/each}}
</td>

</tr>
{{/each}}
</tbody>
</table>


{{outlet}}